event.content:
The San Juan Capistrano Car Show is on for 2021!  So, it will be the 18th Annual event.  And it’s put on by the Rotary of San Juan Capistrano.  This year’s event will feature more than 400 hot rods, muscle cars, classics, imports, trucks, and motorcycles.  Plus this year will include the return of “New Car Row.”

And there’s both a lot planned around the event.  As well as a lot of organizations benefiting from the event.  This makes with it being a Rotary-run experience.

During the show, there will be an Incredible Disc Dog Exhibition.  (I’ve never seen one but it definitely sounds cool!)  Also, the car show will be the terminating location for a Motorcycle Poker Run.

New location: San Juan Hills Golf Club

San Juan Capistrano Car Show

Date: July 10th, 2021
Location: San Juan Hills Golf Club, 32120 San Juan Creek Road, San Juan Capistrano, California, 92675
Starts: 7:30 AM
Ends: 2:00 PM
Admission:
Vehicle Registration:

*Please note: iDriveSoCal does not host this event.  So if you’d like to learn more about the event please contact San Juan Capistrano Car Show organizers HERE.  And that includes more specific details about attending, displaying your vehicle, and becoming a vendor or sponsor.
